00:21:17,916 --> 00:21:18,916
Indeed.

518
00:21:19,000 --> 00:21:20,750
I ask that you remain
close to Ginji

519
00:21:20,833 --> 00:21:22,375
because it truly is dangerous.

520
00:21:22,458 --> 00:21:24,208
Don't wander off without him.

521
00:21:24,291 --> 00:21:25,666
[grumbling]

522
00:21:25,750 --> 00:21:26,958
[AOI]
Hmph!

523
00:21:27,041 --> 00:21:28,333
Hello?!

524
00:21:28,416 --> 00:21:30,000
Is anybody there?!

525
00:21:31,500 --> 00:21:33,583
[AOI]
Okay...

526
00:21:33,666 --> 00:21:34,500
Yah!

527
00:21:37,791 --> 00:21:39,750
Someone! Anyone!

528
00:21:39,833 --> 00:21:41,291
Is anyone there?

529
00:21:41,375 --> 00:21:42,875
