--[gasps]

530
00:21:42,958 --> 00:21:45,875
[DARUMA C] I'm only keeping you
down there for about two days.

531
00:21:45,958 --> 00:21:47,458
--[AOI] Huh?
--[DARUMA C] You know,

532
00:21:47,541 --> 00:21:50,166
until the royal couple's
anniversary has passed.

533
00:21:50,250 --> 00:21:51,541
You what?!

534
00:21:51,625 --> 00:21:53,333
