536
00:21:54,791 --> 00:21:56,416
[AOI gasps]

537
00:21:58,750 --> 00:21:59,708
[thunder claps]

538
00:22:01,125 --> 00:22:02,791
[whimpering]

539
00:22:05,208 --> 00:22:08,166
[crying]

540
00:23:48,958 --> 00:23:50,375
[CHIBI]
Whoa!

541
00:23:50,458 --> 00:23:53,166
